# 7. Plan ကောင်းတစ်ခုမှာ ပါရမယ့်အရာ

Implementation plan ကောင်းတစ်ခုမှာ အောက်ပါအပိုင်းတွေပါသင့်တယ်။

```text
1. Understanding
2. Files to read
3. Files to change
4. Proposed changes
5. Non-goals / out of scope
6. Risks / assumptions
7. Verification plan
8. Rollback plan
9. Approval request
```

## 7.1 Understanding

Agent က task ကိုဘယ်လိုနားလည်ထားလဲပြရမယ်။

```text
Understanding:
User wants to add registration history to a static frontend-only app using localStorage. No backend or package install.
```

## 7.2 Files to Read

```text
Files to read:
- index.html
- style.css
- app.js
```

## 7.3 Files to Change

```text
Files to change:
- index.html: add history list section
- style.css: add history list styling
- app.js: add localStorage and render logic
```

## 7.4 Proposed Changes

```text
Proposed changes:
- Add attendee list container
- Add clear history button
- Add ticket code generator
- Save attendees to localStorage
- Render saved attendees on page load
```

## 7.5 Non-goals

```text
Non-goals:
- No backend API
- No database
- No email/SMS notification
- No package install
```

## 7.6 Risks / Assumptions

```text
Risks:
- localStorage stores phone numbers in browser; privacy consideration.
- If localStorage JSON is corrupted, app should recover safely.

Assumptions:
- This is a learning lab, not production.
```

## 7.7 Verification Plan

```text
Verification:
- Empty name error
- Empty phone error
- Valid registration
- Refresh persistence
- Clear history
- Browser console error check
```

## 7.8 Rollback Plan

```text
Rollback:
- Use git diff to review changes
- Use git restore playground/chapter-11-coding-agent/ if rejected
```

## 7.9 Approval Request

```text
Approval needed:
Please approve this plan before I edit files.
```

