# 18. Plan ထဲမှာ Verification Plan ထည့်ပါ

Verification plan မပါဘဲ implementation plan မပြည့်စုံပါ။

Good verification plan—

```text
Manual tests:
1. Submit empty form → name error
2. Submit name only → phone error
3. Submit valid form → attendee appears
4. Refresh page → attendee remains
5. Clear history → list clears and remains empty after refresh

Static checks:
- Browser console has no errors
- git diff shows only allowed files changed
```

If npm scripts exist—

```text
Commands:
- npm run build
- npm test
```

